definition: Bulgaria/Bulgarian/abbr. for 保加利亞|保加利亚[Bao3 jia1 li4 ya4]
to defend/to protect/to keep/to guarantee/to ensure/civil administration unit in the baojia 保甲[bao3 jia3] system (old)

sentences.english: The premium rate of disproportional reinsurance by bilateral party agreed.
sentences.chinese: 非比例再保险的保险费率由双方当事人议定。

sentences.english: This kind of insurance charge will be according to the cargo.
sentences.chinese: 这类险别的保险费率将根据货物种类而定。

sentences.english: This risk is coverable at a premium of 0.25%.
sentences.chinese: 该险别的保险费是百分之零点二五。

sentences.english: We will deduct the premium from your commission of 5% payable to you.
sentences.chinese: 我们将从支付你方的百分之五的佣金中扣除保险费。

sentences.english: Please give us the policy rates for FPA coverage and for WPA coverage.
sentences.chinese: 请告诉我们平安险和水渍险的保险费率。

sentences.english: I don't care. I need money. I haven't paid into my insurance plan for months.
sentences.chinese: 我不在乎，我需要钱，我有几个月没有交保险费了。

sentences.english: After taxes and insurance, there's not much left to take home.
sentences.chinese: 扣掉税金和保险费后，剩下能带回家的钱就不多了。

sentences.english: The Consignor shall absorb insurance premium and warehousing charges up to the date of delivery to customers.
sentences.chinese: 人负担货物售出之前的保险费和仓储费。

sentences.english: The Credit Class tuition above includes the teaching materials and insurance fee.
sentences.chinese: 学分班以上费用包括补充教材及学生保险费。

sentences.english: Insurance rate of this sort is contingent to the cargo classes.
sentences.chinese: 这类险别的保险费率将根据货物种类而定。

sentences.english: The rate of insurance of this kind vary to the class of the cargo.
sentences.chinese: 这类险别的保险费率将根据货物种类而定。

sentences.english: Please quote us your lowest FPA rates for delivery of fertilizer to Africa.
sentences.chinese: 请保对运往非洲的化肥投保平安险的最低保险费。

sentences.english: We will improve the methods for collecting and managing social security premiums to raise the collection rate.
sentences.chinese: 完善社会保险费征管方式，提高基金征缴率。

sentences.english: They keep back twenty yuan from my salary for insurance.
sentences.chinese: 他们每月从我的工资中扣下二十元钱作为保险费。

sentences.english: Overdue fine will not be charged on the deferred social insurance premium.
sentences.chinese: 缓缴的社会保险费不计收滞纳金。

sentences.english: The cover paid for will vary according to thetypeof goods and the circumstances.
sentences.chinese: 保险费用按照货物类别的详细情况会有所不同。

definition: to pay/to hand over (tax payment etc)
to get out of trouble/to escape from danger/a danger appears/threatened by danger
